{
  "stem": "16887.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 354.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't know what happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Polish-- Poland was always antisemitic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But being that I grew up in a [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Gentile ?] neighborhood, I really didn't feel it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I used to read sometimes in the newspaper, like shortly before the war, the students in the university-- they rebelled against the Jews.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were saying don't buy in Jewish stores.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I, personally, didn't feel it, because I lived a [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Gentile ?] neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, going back to that day, that we got up one day in the morning.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't get undressed, or wash, or anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We just lived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In the daytime, we were staying in the courtyards ready to run.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The night time, we would go down to the cellars.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And one-- after a few days, I said to my husband, I want to go to see if my family's still alive.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My husband got some place a little bit of sugar and some bread.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because when they were bombing, the stores were open.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "People were standing in front, the owners, in front of their stores.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they were begging to take things so they shouldn't burn.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Take [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Take jewelry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Take food.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But nobody thought about it, because everybody was running for-- for their lives.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So who was thinking of taking jewelry or [INAUDIBLE] if you didn't know that the next moment you'll be alive?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we got some sugar and bread in the pocket and some other things I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were going from [NON-ENGLISH] to [NON-ENGLISH], which was-- it was like a mini mall.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was a house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was actually a courtyard that connected two streets, [NON-ENGLISH] and [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's where my aunt lived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We would go-- we start going when it was still curfew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We couldn't go, but we risked.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
